controllercontroller
=======================

Sinatra server for unlimited users to control iTunes remotely. Add/remove tracks from
the playlist, browse the library, control play/pause/volume/etc.


Dependencies
=======================
active_support
sinatra
rb-appscript


Running
=======================

$ ruby server.rb

(C) 2008 Mike Ferrier (mferrier@gmail.com)



CSS + Styles
=======================
by Shawn Allison
I am not supporting or testing this for Internet Explorer, so you can all just DEAL! haha!
Best used in Firefox 3 or Safari.